    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>cd my_gem
</span><span class='line'>mkdir bin
</span><span class='line'>touch bin/my_gem
</span><span class='line'>chmod +x bin/my_gem</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>edit my_gem</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>#!/usr/bin/env ruby
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>require 'my_gem'
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>MyGem.hi</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>edit my_gem.gemspec</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>spec.executables = ["my_gem"]</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>or commit change to git, so you need not change the gemspec file</p>

<p>build and install</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>gem build my_gem.gemspec
</span><span class='line'>gem install --local ./my_gem-0.0.1.gem</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>restart terminal and run</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>my_gem</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
